ata-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532139\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ssj1665702771299.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ssj1665702771299.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ssj1665702771299.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ssj1665702771299\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Remove the specified occurrence from the set of occurrences.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ssj1665702771299__topic_d129356e1_d129357e1_d129358e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ssj1665702771299__p_d129359e1_d129360e1_d129361e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">import\n               com.rocketsoftware.uniface.jci.*;</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ssj1665702771299__p_d129362e1_d129363e1_d129364e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">void removeOccurrence (int</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">occNumber</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ssj1665702771299__section_etr_ysc_dwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1119109e70\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ssj1665702771299__p_d129368e1_d129369e1_d129370e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">occNumber</var>—number of the occurrence.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ssj1665702771299__section_f3y_zsc_dwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1119109e82\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ssj1665702771299__p_d129374e1_d129375e1_d129376e1\">None. <code class=\"ph codeph\">removeOccurrence</code> throws a\n            UnifaceException if there are no occurrences.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ssj1665702771299__section_k5c_btc_dwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1119109e94\">Results</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ssj1665702771299__p_d129380e1_d129381e1_d129382e1\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">occNr</var> is less than zero, the\n            last occurrence in the set is removed. If it is less than or equal to the number of\n            occurrences, the specified occurrence is removed, moving all higher numbered occurrences\n            down by one.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ssj1665702771299__section_u55_ctc_dwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1119109e106\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ssj1665702771299__p_d129386e1_d129387e1_d129388e1\">The behaviour of this method is equivalent to the\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">remocc</code> ProcScript statement.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532139\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532139\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "UnifaceEntity.removeOccurrence Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Remove the specified occurrence from the set of occurrences. import com.rocketsoftware.uniface.jci.*; void removeOccurrence (int occNumber ) Parameters occNumber —number of the occurrence. Return Values None. removeOccurrence throws a UnifaceException if there are no occurrences. Results If occNr is less than zero, the last occurrence in the set is removed. If it is less than or equal to the number of occurrences, the specified occurrence is removed, moving all higher numbered occurrences down by one. Description The behaviour of this method is equivalent to the remocc ProcScript statement. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}